      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/riksbank-kicks-off-easing-with-first-swedish-rate-cut-since-2016</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典央行八年来首次下调基准利率，先于邻国欧元区采取行动，以期为瑞典陷入衰退的经济提供喘息之机。]]></description>
